    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 718 Cayman S is a masterclass in mid-engine engineering, featuring a 2.5L turbocharged boxer-4 equipped with Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG). The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential with Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV). The chassis benefits from the PASM sport suspension, lowered by 20mm for optimal center-of-gravity management. This specimen is in concours-level condition; the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage remains free of any oxidation or fluid seepage. With a documented service history confirming rigorous oil analysis and proactive maintenance, this vehicle offers peak mechanical fidelity for the serious collector.",
