    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, presenting in a state that rivals its original debut on the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of the typical swirls, stone chips, or imperfections found on road-worn examples, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied shortly after purchase. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, showing zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with crisp, factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one. It has never seen a winter, has been strictly hand-washed using the two-bucket method, and comes complete with all original keys, factory manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection and a documented history of care, this example stands alone.",
