    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained valvetrain and recently overhauled VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with Turner plates and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with no signs of oxidation. Performance is sharpened via a bespoke suspension refresh using Bilstein dampers, ensuring the signature 50/50 weight distribution remains precise. A turn-key mechanical masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
